				\begin{document}$z = -0.01z$\end{document} FEB, and (c) in the downstream region. The upper panel shows the spectra simulated in the model with quenched turbulent cascade as it is the case in the models of anisotropic turbulence, while the bottom panel illustrates the magnetic field amplification in the models with the Kolmogorov type cascade

